        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Investor Choice Against Gun Proliferation Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 to require specified issuers of securities to annually disclose any substantial&nbsp;financial relationship with a manufacturer or dealer of firearms or ammunition. </p>]]></text>
